South African N3 Highway Closed Due to Heavy Snow, SAPA Reports

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-07-26T08:54:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/south-african-n3-highway-closed-due-to-heavy-snow-sapa-reports.html
One of  South Africa ’s busiest
highways, the N3 linking Johannesburg, the country’s biggest
city, to the port city of Durban, was closed today because of
heavy snow, the Johannesburg-based South African Press
Association reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
